net.jodah.failsafe

Class AsyncListeners<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.jodah.failsafe.Listeners<T>
      • net.jodah.failsafe.AsyncListeners<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - result type

    public class AsyncListeners<T>
extends Listeners<T>
    Failsafe execution event listeners that are called asynchronously on the Scheduler or ScheduledExecutorService associated with the Failsafe call. To handle completion and failure events, see FailsafeFuture.
